ch.hszt.connectfour.util
Class GameStarter

java.lang.Object
  ch.hszt.connectfour.util.GameStarter

public class GameStarter
extends java.lang.Object

Utility class to trigger relevant logic and actions on starting a Game. Provides different overloads of GameStarter.launch method to initiiate a Game with correct settings.

Version:
1.0, 14.11.2011
Author:
Markus Vetsch
